# Anime Streaming Platform UI Clone

This is a clone of an anime streaming platform UI, specifically showcasing the Kakegurui anime series.

## Setup Instructions

1. Clone this repository
2. Add the image file `kakegurui-banner.jpg` to the root directory
3. Open `index.html` in a web browser

## Required Files
- index.html
- style.css
- kakegurui-banner.jpg (you need to add this)

## Features
- Responsive design
- Modern UI elements
- Hover effects
- Mobile-friendly navigation

## Note
This is a static UI implementation. For a full working platform, you would need to implement:
- Backend functionality
- User authentication
- Video streaming capabilities
- Database integration 